WHI Abuse and Sexual Function

Sidebar

All analyses include information from women who participated in the WHI, gave a “yes” or “no” response to the two questions related to abuse, and reported being sexually active in the previous year.

Please use the navigation bar (blue bar at the top of the screen) to view:
